longBusinessSummary: Bredband2 i Skandinavien AB (publ) provides data communication and security solutions to individuals and companies in Sweden. It offers router subscriptions, security packages, streaming, network, telephony/exchange services including mobile telephony, internet services, mobile broadband, and data center services. The company was incorporated in 1989 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
